Terrorsaur:





Terrorsaur took of, transforming to beast mode while in mid flight. He 
circled the area, keeping a keen eye out. He said into his comm-link to 
Quickstrike: "Situation clear. The Maximal has retreated."

"Is Stingtra alright?" the scorpion hybrid asked.

"Yeah," he said. "She's fine."
